getShortestPath

public List<E> getShortestPath(V v1,
                               V v2)
Returns a List containing the nodes of the shortest path between v1 and v2, not including v1. The size of this List will be the length of the path.

Parameters:
v1 - The node to start at.
v2 - The node to end with.
Returns:
A List containing the shortest path, or null if no such path exists.
